:GRAPH Lagrange_Polynomial
:TITLE Lagrange Polynomial
:X-AXIS x
:X-DIV 1
:SCALE
:VAR y

:GRAPH VECTOR_LOOKUP
:TITLE VECTOR LOOKUP
:X-AXIS x
:X-DIV 1
:SCALE
:VAR VECTOR LOOKUP y
:SCALE
:VAR smooth VECTOR LOOKUP y

:GRAPH Cubic_Spline
:TITLE Cubic Spline
:X-AXIS x
:X-DIV 1
:SCALE
:VAR spline y
